                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note, written in the main hand, mentions the scribe Wäldä Muse, the commissioner Wäldä Mikaʾel and his family members as well as gäbäz Wäldä ʾAnanya.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
